Who We Are
Our Clients



Our Firm Savant Capital, LLC is an independent registered investment advisor.  Based in San Francisco, Savant Capital provides financial advice and wealth management services to institutions, retirement plans, and affluent individuals. We are dedicated to helping our clients secure their financial goals and well-being.  We offer our select clients a unique combination of top-tier financial advice and investment management, as well as excellent service.  
Savant Capital strives to deliver superior  long-term capital appreciation within a managed risk context for our client portfolios. We apply an extensive global  analytical framework and a bottom-up fundamental approach to identify the most promising investment opportunities.  We seek to capitalize on market inefficiencies across industries, companies, and geographies. We use sophisticated risk-management techniques  to reduce portfolio volatility and preserve capital.


