Intern Program




















Opportunity to Gain Valuable Experience







Our internship program provides high school and college students with the opportunity to gain experience in the financial industry. Each intern's assignment is based on his/her interests and our company needs. These assignments are important to Savant’s business, and offer interns the opportunity to contribute substantially.

Our interns find that there are many advantages to accepting a summer internship at Savant. Interns are assigned projects that help meet important business needs, but also offer challenging and unique opportunities for interns to learn, grow, and succeed. Our interns have been involved in trading, investment analysis, marketing, database maintenance, investment research, financial planning research, market research, cash flow analysis, excel modeling, launching new offices, and much more.

Our interns have the opportunity to extend their internship into winter and spring. Some interns even come back and end up at Savant full-time. However, all would agree that their internships at Savant provide a unique opportunity to learn and grow as they build their ideal careers.

In One Intern's Words:
“I believe Savant has provided me with a great understanding of today’s market, along with the skills needed to make decisions and interact with others.  Prior to working at Savant, I viewed internships as making copies, making coffee, and avoiding mistakes, but at Savant, I have learned, grown, and developed a clear understanding of what a real internship should be.”


View Open Internships and Apply Now




















