Join Savant



















Savant is a financial advisory and planning firm headquartered in Illinois, with additional offices in Wisconsin and Virginia (D.C. Metro). We are among the fastest growing independent registered investment advisors in the nation. Team Savant consists of distinct departments with an array of career paths available: Accounting, Administrative, Advisory, Compliance, Client Services, Financial Planning, Human Resources, Ideal Retirement Plan Services, Implementation Services, Information Technology, Investment Research, Marketing, Tax & Consulting, and Trading. Whether you are a highly experienced financial advisor or a college student taking advantage of the Savant Internship Program, there may be an opportunity for you.

At Savant, we believe our collective expertise can provide greater solutions than any individual could hope to offer on their own. Because of this, we utilize a team-based approach. Team Savant is structured to provide outstanding service while insulating clients from the myriad details associated with day-to-day procedures. Our unique culture and team structure make Savant an attractive organization to start or continue your career.

We understand the importance of a supporting environment that encourages employee engagement. Recognized as one of the 2016 Best Places to Work in Illinois, Savant is committed to providing a team-oriented and rewarding place to work. We foster a family-like culture where employees genuinely care about our clients and each other.

