Careers























At Savant, we hire people who fit within the culture that we have built and maintained since we were founded in 1986. Our team members share a common passion – serving our clients– and they do so with the highest level of integrity and care. When searching for new team members, we look for individuals who demonstrate a servant leadership attitude and an aptitude to serve the needs of others before themselves. We want to work alongside individuals who are smart, talented, energetic, positive, and team oriented.  We believe in…



Providing the greatest value possible for our clients through seamless execution of our day-to-day responsibilities
Offering world class investment and planning advice
Constantly evolving and using our collective knowledge and expertise to meet our clients’ needs
Being surrounded by a supportive team that makes it easy to excel
Encouraging our employees to pursue ongoing education and renewed commitment to excellence
Employing exceptionally talented, team-oriented individuals
Seeking individuals with a sense of integrity and highly ethical behavior



