Team



















Functioning much like the Mayo Clinic, Savant has hired the best and brightest specialists to create a synergistic and integrated team that is more effective collectively, than separately. The Advisory Team functions like the doctors who diagnose and prescribe; the Concierge Team functions like nurses who coordinate and manage work flow; the Implementation Team are like the pharmacists who fill the prescriptions to make client portfolios feel better; and the Administrative Team supervises and supports the other teams. See glossary of professional designations.









 

